camps.name: Mountain View Campground
camps.about:
Enjoy stunning views of the mountains at this campsite.

Our six-acre solar-powered goat farm is a quiet and peaceful slice of paradise away from the chaos and noise but close to so many places to adventure.

Spring is in the air and goats are having kids (babies). Visit during March or April and you may just see a live birth plus play with baby goats!  Feed and play with the goats, picnic along our grass-covered brook, hang out around the large fire pit, and rejuvenate while being close to the many Smoky and Blue Ridge Mountain activities.
